"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-18-CMG-preparing-to-provide-first-class-reports-on-2024-Paris-Olympics-1vkth64wBXy-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Members of the China Media Group's working staff prepare for the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999280491946, \"rank\": 7.195081909923573e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CMG  The China Media Group (CMG), as one of the primary broadcasters for the upcoming 2024 Summer Olympics, has dispatched a production and broadcasting team of more than 2,000 people to Paris.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_Georg