http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG began to set up its ultra-high-definition broadcasting system at the location shooting site and television studio at the Eiffel Tower and IBC on July 3.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9757210777705707, \"rank\": 0.024882775416761444, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The construction work is expected to be completed by Saturday.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CMG will deploy nearly 40 media convergence groups at different venues during the 2024 Summer Olympics, ready to provide first-class, professional reports to its audience through a series of premium programs.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9757210777705707, \"rank\": 0.024882775416761444, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": []}]}"